s state-of-the-art SVS\nwork. Extensional experiments also prove the generalization of our methods on\ntext-to-speech task (DiffSpeech). Audio samples: https://diffsinger.github.io.\nCodes: https://github.com/MoonInTheRiver/DiffSinger. The old title of this\nwork: \"Diffsinger: Diffusion acoustic model for singing voice synthesis\".\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 05:21:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 30 May 2021 13:24:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 12 Dec 2021 12:56:46 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 06:22:20 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2022 09:08:03 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 04:53:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-23"}
