\mathcal F$). Interesting\nopen problems remain, in particular completing the determination of\n$k(P,\\mathcal F)$ for the three parameters: the independence number,\nindependent domination number and domination number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 07:52:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 14:59:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2022 09:51:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-14"}
