 C$_{60}$, where vdW effects are\nimportant. The need for a highly accurate vdW-inclusive reactive force field is\nhighlighted by modeling the decomposition of the C$_{60}$ molecules taking\nplace at high pressures and temperatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 08:54:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Jul 2021 11:00:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Aug 2021 12:34:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
